Xinhua News Agency, Beijing, July 25 (Reporters Yu Junjie and Chen Aiping) Reporters learned from the National Cyberspace Administration on the 25th that the governance of illegal collection and use of personal information by App in 2020 was officially launched recently, focusing on cracking down on issues such as private uploading of personal information in the background of App.
