In the first half of this year, in the face of the impact of the COVID-19 pneumonia epidemic, China made a concerted effort to promote epidemic prevention and control and economic and social development. The epidemic prevention and control situation continued to improve, the steady economic recovery was obvious, the employment and price performance closely related to people's livelihood were generally stable, and the Chinese economy handed over a report card of economic operation with temperature.
In the first two months of this year, the surveyed unemployment rate rose.
Especially in February, the production and operation activities of many enterprises were basically in a state of shutdown, the employment demand of enterprises decreased, recruitment was delayed or cancelled, and the urban survey unemployment rate increased.
With the gradual improvement of the epidemic prevention and control situation, the production and living order of the whole society has been continuously restored.
The CPC Central Committee adheres to the general tone of the work of stability and progress, further increases macro-policy hedging, comprehensively strengthens the employment priority policy, and actively promotes the work of assisting and stabilizing jobs and expanding employment.
China has increased its policies to hedge and stabilize jobs, played a combination of " relief, relief, slow return and compensation " policies, reduced and exempted the payment parts of three social insurance units in stages, allowed the postponement of the payment of social insurance premiums, expanded the benefits of unemployment insurance return and work-for-training policies for small and medium-sized enterprises, and provided absorption subsidies and internship subsidies to enterprises to absorb the employment of key groups.
With the implementation of various stable employment policies, the employment demand of enterprises has steadily picked up, the employment situation has gradually improved, and the surveyed unemployment rate in cities and towns has gradually decreased. In June, the surveyed unemployment rate was 5.7%.
Zhang Yi, director of the Population and Employment Statistics Department of the National Bureau of Statistics, said that in the second quarter, various employment policies continued to bear fruit, and the labor force that withdrew in the early period due to the impact of the epidemic returned one after another. The urban labor participation rate in June increased by about 10 percentage points compared with February, which is close to the level of the same period last year.
Data show that the total urban employment in June increased by more than 19% compared with February, and most industries reached the pre-epidemic level; the average weekly working hours of employees in enterprises reached 46.8 hours, 6.6 hours higher than in February and 0.1 hours higher than in January.
Prices also concern thousands of households.
In January this year, the CPI rose by 5.4% year-on-year, setting a new high for many years.
In February, although the year-on-year increase of CPI fell slightly, it was still in the " 5 range. "
The year-on-year increase of CPI is at a high level, which is driven by consumer demand before the Spring Festival, as well as the wrong month of the Spring Festival and a low year-on-year base.
However, the impact of the COVID-19 pneumonia epidemic on prices is particularly obvious.
Affected by the prevention and control of the epidemic, logistics delays, untimely supply of materials and increased transportation costs occurred in all parts of the country in January and February. In addition, some citizens hoarded and snapped up, and the prices of some basic necessities increased significantly.
In order to cope with the disturbance caused by epidemic prevention and control to the price situation, relevant departments have included important living materials in the scope of emergency transportation guarantee to ensure the smooth transportation of materials.
Under the effect of a series of policy measures, the market supply of vegetables, melons and fruits has been strongly guaranteed.
